<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Pricing Cards</title>
    <!-- Material Tailwind stylesheet -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://unpkg.com/@material-tailwind/html@latest/styles/material-tailwind.css"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white">
    <!-- CONTENEDOR CENTRAL DE LAS CARDS -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 w-full px-4 my-8">

      <!-- CARD 1 - Viajes Particulares -->
      <div class="relative flex w-full max-w-[20rem] flex-col rounded-xl bg-[#0e0a3a] p-8 text-[#FFD700] shadow-[0_0_60px_#0e0a3a] min-h-[350px]">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-8 border-b border-[#FFD700]/20 pb-8">
          <!-- Ícono auto o ruta (opcional, se puede reemplazar por uno que prefieras) -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            class="w-10 h-10 text-[#FFD700] mb-2">
            <path d="M3 12l2-2 4 4 8-8 2 2-10 10z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="mt-2 text-4xl">Viajes Particulares</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-[#FFD700]/30 bg-[#FFD700]/10 p-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-3 w-3 text-[#FFD700]">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-base">Traslados desde y hacia el aeropuerto de Santiago.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-[#FFD700]/30 bg-[#FFD700]/10 p-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-3 w-3 text-[#FFD700]">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-base">Servicios por hora.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-[#FFD700]/30 bg-[#FFD700]/10 p-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-3 w-3 text-[#FFD700]">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-base">Servicios por día, vehículo exclusivo para movilizarse dentro y fuera de Santiago.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- CARD 2 - Confianza -->
      <div class="relative flex w-full max-w-[20rem] flex-col rounded-xl bg-[#0e0a3a] p-8 text-[#FFD700] shadow-[0_0_60px_#0e0a3a] min-h-[350px]">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-8 border-b border-[#FFD700]/20 pb-8">
          <!-- Ícono apretón de manos -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            class="w-10 h-10 text-[#FFD700] mb-2">
            <path d="M2.5 8.5L6 12l3.5-3.5L6 5.5 2.5 8.5zm19 0L18 5.5l-3.5 3.5L18 12l3.5-3.5zm-8.5 4.5l-2 2-2-2 2-2 2 2z" />
          </svg>
          <span class="mt-2 text-4xl">Confianza</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-center text-center">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-[#FFD700]/30 bg-[#FFD700]/10 p-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-3 w-3 text-[#FFD700]">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-base">Más de 10 años prestando un servicio de alto estándar en vehículos que garantizan confort y lujo.</p>
          </li>
           <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-[#FFD700]/30 bg-[#FFD700]/10 p-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-3 w-3 text-[#FFD700]">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-base">Línea directa para asistencia en cualquier momento del viaje.</p>
          </li> 
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- CARD 3 - Seguridad -->
      <div class="relative flex w-full max-w-[20rem] flex-col rounded-xl bg-[#0e0a3a] p-8 text-[#FFD700] shadow-[0_0_60px_#0e0a3a] min-h-[350px]">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-8 border-b border-[#FFD700]/20 pb-8">
          <!-- Ícono escudo -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            class="w-10 h-10 text-[#FFD700] mb-2">
            <path d="M12 2C7 4 4 4 4 4v5c0 5.25 3.25 9.75 8 11 4.75-1.25 8-5.75 8-11V4s-3 0-8-2z" />
          </svg>
          <span class="mt-2 text-4xl">Seguridad</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-center text-center">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-[#FFD700]/30 bg-[#FFD700]/10 p-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-3 w-3 text-[#FFD700]">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-base">Priorizamos la seguridad de los pasajeros en todos los aspectos del servicio.</p>
          </li> 
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-[#FFD700]/30 bg-[#FFD700]/10 p-1">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-3 w-3 text-[#FFD700]">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-base">Disponibilidad para traslados urgentes o de último minuto con respuesta inmediata.</p>
          </li> 
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ripple effect script -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@material-tailwind/html@latest/scripts/ripple.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
